#Signuture @resort_and_hotel
Location: Oku Hotel is located in #Ibiza, #Spain. The Oku hotel showcase the best of classic modernist design coupled with beachside flair. Natural textures teamed with local stone and wood, create inviting private sanctuaries and indulgent communal spaces where guests relax and switch off in style. Photographed by @Okuhotels 
 .
Would you love to be here? 😍

Warm wishes
@adriankays

node.text:
#Signuture
Share you thoughts with us!
A million Times is an ongoing project that continues the conceptual exploration of one of Humans. The hands of multiple analogue clocks are programmed to move independently and in formation to perform abstract, dance-like choreographies, before synchronising once each minute to accurately tell the time in a digital typography. Designed by @humanssince1982 
 

Warm wishes
@adriankays
__
